OL,3,COfficer shot by police firearm during
OL,4,Cmachete arrest
OL,6,FA police officer in Gloucester has
OL,7,Fbeen shot in the leg by a police
OL,8,Ffirearm after a struggle involving a
OL,9,Fman with a machete.
OL,11,FGloucestershire Constabulary officers
OL,12,Fwere called to reports that a taxi
OL,13,Fdriver had been robbed by a man with a
OL,14,Fmachete at around 4.40pm on Wednesday
OL,15,F17 September.
OL,17,FArmed officers located the suspect
OL,18,Finside a block of flats on Silverstone
OL,19,FWalk. The man struggled with officers
OL,20,Fas they tried to detain him, and a
OL,21,Fpolice firearm was discharged.
