OL,6,FOne man was arrested and remains in
OL,7,Fcustody. The force has not yet
OL,8,Fclarified who shot the weapon.
OL,10,FThe injured officer was taken to
OL,11,Fhospital, and his wound is not
OL,12,Fbelieved to be life-threatening.
OL,14,FTemporary Chief Constable Maggie Blyth
OL,15,Fsaid: "My thoughts are with the
OL,16,Fofficer who's been injured and his
OL,17,Fcolleague following this incident.
