OL,6,F"I am grateful for the bravery they
OL,7,Fhave shown in detaining someone
OL,8,Fsuspected of carrying out a robbery
OL,9,Fand possessing a machete and who was
OL,10,Fbelieved to have been a real danger to
OL,11,Fthe public."
OL,13,FIan White, Secretary of
OL,14,FGloucestershire Police Federation,
OL,15,Fadded: "Police officers in
OL,16,FGloucestershire - and across the
OL,17,Fcountry - work in an incredibly
OL,18,Fdifficult, dynamic and dangerous
OL,19,Fenvironment, often faced with severe
OL,20,Fthreat and danger.
