OL,6,F"We wish our colleague injured in
OL,7,FKingsway last night a swift recovery.
OL,8,FWe will be supporting the officer and
OL,9,Ftheir family and looking after the
OL,10,Fwelfare of all the officers involved
OL,11,Fin the incident."
OL,13,FA cordon has been put in place, and
OL,14,Fpolice officers will remain in the
OL,15,Farea to provide reassurance to the
OL,16,Fpublic.
OL,18,FThe incident has been referred to the
OL,19,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct.
